---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Jhoni Pereira">
	<main class="container mx-auto px-5 md:px-0 md:max-w-6xl">
		

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 justify-center align-items-center mt-16 mb-10 relative">
			
			<div class="text-2xl col-span-2 text-center md:text-left bg-slate-700 border-slate-600 md:-mx-10 md:-my-8 px-2 md:px-10 md:py-8 md:pb-0 border-2 ">
				<h1 class="font-bold text-5xl mb-5 mt-2">
					<span class="block">👋🏾 Hi there!</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="">I'm a software developer with 12 years of experience in web development, and I'm all about solving problems and creating awesome applications for people.</p>
				<br>
				<p class="mb-5">Besides coding, I have a passion for my family, sports, fitness, culinary, TV series, and my beloved dog 🐶.</p>
				
			</div>
			<div class="text-center mb-6 md:mb-0 order-first md:order-last">
				<img src="/profile.png" alt="Jhoni Pereira" class="rounded-full md:rounded-none max-w-xs inline-block shadow-xl md:w-full">
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto my-4 md:mt-24 text-center md:text-left">
			<h2 class="font-bold text-5xl mb-5 md:mb-8">About Me</h2>

			<article class="mb-10 md:mb-16 content text-2xl">
				<p>Currently, I work remotely at <a href="https://www.tidea.com.br/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Tidea</a>, helping organizations shape their technology visions, execute their digital transformation journeys, and reinvent their businesses to create value from their technology investments.</p>
				
				<p>⌛️ Over the past 12 years, I've worked with HTML, CSS, SASS, Javascript, jQuery, PHP and Laravel.</p>

				<p>✅ I've been working with React and Next.js for <span>about 3 years</span>.</p>

				<p>🚀 My journey takes an exciting turn as I transition from Frontend to Backend domains. The allure of backend technologies and intricate architecture deeply engages my curiosity. I have my sights set not only on mastering PHP but also diving into Golang, and the captivating world of blockchain and AI.</p>
				
				<p>Feel free to check out my <a href="#portfolio">portfolio</a>.</p>
				
			</article>
			<article class="mb-10 md:mb-16 content text-2xl">
				<h2 class="font-bold text-5xl mb-5 md:mb-8">Industries I have worked in:</h2>
				
				<p>I have over twelve years of experience working for large to small organisations in: Health, Events, Digital Products, Lawtech, Real State, Insurance & Educational.</p>
			</article>

			<article id="portfolio" class="mb-10 md:mb-16 content text-2xl">
				<h2 class="font-bold text-5xl mb-5 md:mb-8">Portfolio</h2>
				
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
					<Card
						href="https://www.vpgclubedebeneficios.com.br/"
						title="VPG Benefits Club (React, Next.js) "
						body=""
						image="/portfolio/1.jpg"
					/>
					<Card
						href="https://www.dentsplysirona.com/pt-br"
						title="Forte Beer App (React Native)"
						body=""
						image="/portfolio/2.jpg"
					/>
					<Card
						href="https://apps.apple.com/lc/app/forte-beer/id1589865870"
						title="Dentsply Sirona (PHP)"
						body=""
						image="/portfolio/3.jpg"
					/>
					<Card
						href="https://www.eduzz.com/pt-br/produtos/blinket"
						title="Eduzz, Blinket (PHP, Laravel, JS, React)"
						body=""
						image="/portfolio/4.jpg"
					/>
					
				</div>
				
			</article>
		</div>

	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.instructions {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
		background-color: white;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.4rem;
	}
	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.875em;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 12%);
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.3em 0.45em;
	}
	.instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
